folder: College Place & Love Lane, Brooklyn, NY
text:
17-19 College Place, west side, near Love Lane; a view of 2-frame houses, since razed.

1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster collection.

A general view, southeast from the Hotel St. George. (No. 51 Clark Street), showing the German Evang. Lutheran Church (left), and the Church of the Pilgrim's (right). Shown in the foreground, is College Place, east side, south to Love Lane. This set consists of three views taken at the same time.

June 15, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.
title: General View - Brooklyn - Hotel St. George.
